=== ECHO_CHAMBER ===
# id: 4
# title: The Echo Chamber
# chinese_title: 回声
# category: Discovery
# mode: dungeon

You enter a spherical room where every sound multiplies into a thousand whispers. The chamber was designed for deep-space communication relay, but now it amplifies even your breathing into an eerie chorus. Embedded in the walls are resonance crystals worth a small fortune.

* [Carefully remove some crystals]
  ~ gain_gold(30)
  "声" (shēng) — sound, voice
* [Listen to the echoes — they seem to form patterns]
  ~ gain_radical("口")
  "口" (kǒu) — mouth, opening
* [Use the relay to send a signal]
  ~ gain_xp(15)
  "信" (xìn) — message, trust, believe
